{"type": "article", "id": 22322, "title": "双面三维项链", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-16T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021257126ZM7eycDt20oAaKv.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">希腊的艺术家 Eleftheria Stamati 设计了一根双面穿戴的项链，其实是披在肩上的。吊坠利用几何原理和透视关系设计出带有立体感的图案，像是一个长方体或多个长方体，并特意空出了一根支柱，搭配着很细的链子，有种空灵感。正反两个吊坠恰好朝着两个不同的方向，突出了它的立方体视觉感受。<br></p>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021257109VwsCgNQeUDvGJZW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125710byxWFdevg6aV29iN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125710wb3nt1PExolVuk2e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021257116HLrZDjuWpgTGYwI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}